the two\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9781,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/11\/prophet-forbearing-forgiving\/","url_meta":{"origin":9922,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: The Prophet was forbearing, forgiving","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 11, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was not presented with two matters but that he would choose the easier of them, as long as it was not sinful. If it was sinful, he would be the furthest of people from it. The Prophet did\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33106,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/first-thing-prophet-does\/","url_meta":{"origin":9922,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Siwak: First thing the Prophet does at home","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Shurayh reported: I asked Aisha, saying, \u201cWhat was the first thing the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, did when he entered his house?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cUse the toothstick.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 253 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0634\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062d\u064d \u0633\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0644\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064f\u0644\u0652\u062a\u064f \u